    Graphic Designer

    Worked as a graphic designer on various Bollywood feature films, contributing to visual storytelling through print and digital assets.
    Projects: Fan, Rustom

    Assistant Art Director

    Assisted in the art direction and production design of major film productions and contributed to set execution and design aesthetics.
    Projects: Satyameva Jayate, Babumoshai Bandookbaaz, Blank, Darbar

    Art Director

    Led the art department, overseeing the creative vision, set design, and execution from concept to final production across films and series.
    Projects: Mere Desh Ki Dharti, Kurup, Satyameva Jayate 2, The Trial, Union: The Making of India (upcoming), Matka King (upcoming), Diler (upcoming)

    Assistant Production Designer

    Collaborated with the production design team to support creative and technical implementation of large-scale sets.
    Project: The Empire

    Associate Production Designer

    Supported the design team in executing large-scale sets, handling construction, set dressing, visual detailing, and involvement in budgeting and material planning.
    Projects: Babli Bouncer, Blackout, Kaun Banegi Shikharwati
